gaged (zero calls, emails, tasks in 52 days). No budget discussion, no commercial conversation, no CFO meeting occurred despite Ellen's stated intent to review internally. If CFO does not sponsor this initiative, deal cannot progress beyond Qualified.", "role": "Economic Buyer", "title": "Executive Vice-President and Chief Financial Officer", "sentiment": "Unknown (never engaged)", "last_contact_date": null}, {"name": "Ellen Powell", "risk": "Single point of contact and only engaged stakeholder, but positioned as Influencer (not Decision Maker or Champion). Initiated contact and expressed interest 14 May but immediately deferred evaluation ('right now is probably not the best time, we've got some big projects in the works'). Stated she would review with CFO/CEO but no evidence that review occurred. Silent for 34 days since 1 June. Has not demonstrated active championship (no CFO intro, no internal docs shared, no urgency). If Ellen goes quiet or deprioritizes, deal goes dark.", "role": "Influencer", "title": "Director of Supply Chain", "sentiment": "Neutral to cooling", "last_contact_date": "2026-06-01"}]}, "meddpicc": {"metrics": {"status": "gap", "sources": ["Avoma discovery call 14 May 2026 (Ellen Powell)", "SF Next_Step__c (current): Bailey to send ROI business case form", "SF Customer_Business_Problem__c, Business_Objectives__c, Value_to_Customer__c: empty"], "narrative": "No quantified business case or financial impact stated by the buyer across the single discovery call (14 May) or any Salesforce field. Ellen Powell articulated general interest in procurement digitization and mentioned 'big projects in the works' as the reason for deferral, but provided no cost savings target, cycle-time reduction goal, headcount impact, error-rate baseline, or ROI threshold. Customer_Business_Problem__c, Business_Objectives__c, Value_to_Customer__c, and Pain_points_in_the_current_solution__c fields are all empty. The deal owner committed to sending an ROI business case form 